<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka leisiet hinkhuo beih a tuisanglien gal ka kaih tieng,
 Zing khawvak hawih lopitak chu ka muh tieng;
 Ka Tanpa chuh he'ng ka luigal langkhat chuh ka tun tieng,
 A mel deihum chun kei ei na lawp ina.

[V2]
 Amah he'ng ka, Amah he'ng ka,
 Tatsa, A kawma ka din tieng leh;
 Amah he'ng ka, Amah he'ng ka,
 A khut thikkilh sutna chun he'ng ka.

[V3]
 2. A mel deihum ka muh tieng ka thagau kipak ina,
 Chun, A hehpihna mai eng chuh ka muh tieng;
 Bangtibang phetin ka pak dem ei lungsietna ziekin,
 Vana umna ding In ei Siemsakpa chuh.

[V4]
 2. Lopina muna deihtakte'n chieh dingin ei sam ui,
 Thihna luia ka kikhen petuh ka hei;
 Eden tuol nuom achun ei lamtuohna di'n la sa'n au,
 Mahleh Hukdampa tuok masak pen ka nuom.

[V5]
 4. Puon lopi nin beklo silh a khawpi kawt ka lut tieng,
 Mitthi luon tak lohna ah ei pui intin;
 Kumsawt nawpna lasa'n keile kipakin tel tang ka,
 Mahleh Hukdampa tuok masak pen ka nuom.</lyrics>
<title>I SHALL KNOW HIM</title>
<hymn_number>375</hymn_number>
</song>